  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/peripherals/\" rel=\"tag\">外围设备</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/08/scanadu-scout-tricorder-hands-on/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/e7ab40b44400df4a25d75d5cf8eb4e98/DSC09744%20copy.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n问世于 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2012/11/29/scanadu-scout-tricorder/\">2012</a> 年、之后在 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/06/18/scanadu-scout-tricorder-tops-1-million-in-funding/\">Indiegogo</a> 上筹得 100 万美元的健康扫描仪 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/05/22/scanadu-scout-tricorder-final-design/\">Scanadu Scout</a>，在 3 月末时就会被送到那些初期资助者的手中，而其最终的硬件形态也于今天早些时候在 CES 会场中揭晓。上图中这两款就是最终的成品，它们拿起来很轻，摸起来做工很好。至于功能，只要将其放到额头前碰触几秒钟，体温、心率、血压等身体数据就会被发送到相关的应用中，让用户对自己的身体状况有一个大致的了解。<br />\n<br />\nScanadu 创始人、CEO Walter de Brouwer 在接受我们采访时表示，他和手下团队设想中的环形设计实在是太难以打造，他们花了相当大的功夫才能得到现有的成果。不知道各位对这个造型感觉如何，要是你对这款产品感兴趣的话，图集中有更多照片，你也可以看看仍在开发中的应用截图喔。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/scanadu-scout-tricorder-and-app-screenshots/\">Scanadu Scout tricorder and app screenshots</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/scanadu-scout-tricorder-and-app-screenshots/6431000/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc09730-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/scanadu-scout-tricorder-and-app-screenshots/6431001/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc09731-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/scanadu-scout-tricorder-and-app-screenshots/6431002/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc09733-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/scanadu-scout-tricorder-and-app-screenshots/6431003/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc09735-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/scanadu-scout-tricorder-and-app-screenshots/6431004/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/dsc09737-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/07/scanadu-scout-tricorder-hands-on/\">Engadget</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/08/scanadu-scout-tricorder-hands-on/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20803297/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/08/scanadu-scout-tricorder-hands-on/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
